Django Grappelli
================
.. image:: https://api.travis-ci.org/sehmaschine/django-grappelli.svg
    :target: https://travis-ci.org/sehmaschine/django-grappelli

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/dm/django-grappelli.svg
